-= Kitchen =-
You've just walked into a kitchen.

Oh wow! Is that what I think it is? It is! It's a fridge. Suddenly, you bump your head on the ceiling, but it's not such a bad bump that it's going to prevent you from looking at objects and even things. You can make out a closed oven close by. What's that over there? It looks like it's a table. You see a cookbook on the table. You can make out a counter. Wow, isn't TextWorld just the best? On the counter you can make out a banana, a raw red potato and a knife. I mean, just wow! Isn't TextWorld just the best? You can make out a stove. The stove is conventional. However, the stove, like an empty stove, has nothing on it. What, you think everything in TextWorld should have stuff on it?
